title: Sasheer May Be Joining the Spectacle Brigade
description:
Nicole has questions for Farm Rio, she loves them, but what is her true ordering size? Sasheer watched Dahmer and both Nicole and her agreed, yikes! However, they do like Joe and are excited for YOU. They take a quiz about what their eyes say about them, and lastly answer some questions with their natural  born leader abilities.

 

Here is the quiz from this week: 

https://www.quizyourfriends.com/what-do-your-eyes-say-about-you/
